[IMG]http://i55.tinypic.com/2mp0qk5.png[/img][URL=http://sabsabionline.com]Home[/URL] [IMG]http://i52.tinypic.com/210admu.png[/img][URL=http://sabsabionline.com/forum.php]Forums[/URL]
[B][SIZE=4]Why play SabsabiOnline?[/SIZE][/B] Well I can start off by saying that SabsabiOnline is a veteran server in the RSPS scene and used to be the biggest server that was running back in 2010, we had partnered up with google at that time and was running with a steady playercount of 1500 dvided up across 3 worlds. Now we aren't so big, we have just released our beta version of the game, and it's averaging 5 - 20 players, without advertisement! We have a TON of old school runescape content and flawless combat. We strive for the perfect version of a economical yet also PK server.
